explanations.reason: The paper focuses on the impact of the Sustainable Finance Disclosure Regulation (SFDR) on greenwashing by equity mutual funds in the EU, using measures like the Greenwashing Index and statistical methods such as difference-in-differences analysis and regression discontinuity design (RDD). There is no mention of any machine learning techniques, algorithms, or models in the title or abstract, nor any indication that such methods were used in the research.
